\sum_{n=1}^\infty ln\big[1+\big(\dfrac{1}{n}\big)\big](x+2)^n
\lim_{n\to\infty} \dfrac{|a_{n+1}|}{|a_n|} = \lim_{n\to\infty} \dfrac{ln\big[1+\big(\dfrac{1}{n+1}\big)\big]|x+2|^{n+1}}{ln\big[1+\big(\dfrac{1}{n}\big)\big]|x+2|^n} = \lim_{n\to\infty} \dfrac{ln\big[1+\big(\dfrac{1}{n+1}\big)\big]}{ln\big[1+\big(\dfrac{1}{n}\big)\big]} \cdot |x+2|
\lim_{n\to\infty} \dfrac{ln\big[1+\big(\dfrac{1}{n+1}\big)\big]}{ln\big[1+\big(\dfrac{1}{n}\big)\big]} = \lim_{n\to\infty} \dfrac{n}{2+n} = 1
\lim_{n\to\infty} \dfrac{ln\big[1+\big(\dfrac{1}{n+1}\big)\big]}{ln\big[1+\big(\dfrac{1}{n}\big)\big]} \cdot |x+2| = |x+2|
|x+2| \lt 1
|x+2| \gt 1
